聆听汤姆·格伦南 (Tom Grennan) 令人振奋的新单曲“Higher” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-tom-grennans-new-single-higher-3795435?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-tom-grennans-new-single-higherTom Skinner Fri, 20 Sep 2024 07:23:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3795435 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="汤姆·格伦南新闻照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在制作第四张录音室专辑时，他受到乔治·迈克尔和普林斯等标志性艺术家的启发：“很多人不知道他们会受到什么打击”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-tom-grennans-new-single-higher-3795435">聆听 Tom Grennan 令人振奋的新单曲“Higher”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="汤姆·格伦南新闻照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/TomGrennan-releases-new-single-Higher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-grennan">汤姆·格伦南 (Tom Grennan)</a>分享了一首名为“Higher”的新单曲 - 您可以在下面收听。</p><p>这首流畅而振奋人心的歌曲将出现在这位创作型歌手尚未公布的第四张专辑中，该专辑将继 2023 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-grennan-announces-new-album-what-ifs-maybes-and-2023-uk-arena-tour-3318814">《What Ifs &amp; Maybes》</a>之后。</p><p>这首受“流行艺术”启发的歌曲在伦敦传奇的 RAK 录音室录制，以朗朗上口的钢琴连复段开始。</p><p> “我的奇怪之处在于，我在录音室里创作音乐，但我的大多数好主意都是在我实际上不在录音室里时想到的，”格伦南在一份声明中解释道。</p><p> “在我们写《Higher》的那天，我离开了房间，但我就是无法将那个即兴重复段从我的脑海中抹去。它变成了旋律，又变成了短语……我跑回录音室，钢琴连复段仍在演奏，举起双手唱道：“<em>它让我更高</em>”。</p><p>他总结道：“房间里的每个人都说：‘繁荣’。就是这样&#39;。”</p><p>在这里查看官方歌词视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="汤姆·格伦南 (Tom Grennan) - 《Higher》（歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yocP0mZoyk4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>至于粉丝们对他的下一个时代的总体期望，格伦南开玩笑说：“很多人不知道他们会受到什么打击。”</p><p>这位艺术家一直在与词曲作者兼制作人贾斯汀·特兰特（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/britney-spears">布兰妮·斯皮尔斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">林肯公园</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fall-out-boy">打倒男孩</a>）合作创作新材料，贾斯汀·特兰特“准确地理解了他想说的内容和他想要听起来的样子”。</p><p>一份新闻稿引用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-michael">乔治·迈克尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">普林斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/freddie-mercury">弗雷迪·墨丘利</a>等标志性艺术家作为格伦南即将推出的音乐的参考。</p><p> “很多新音乐都是令人振奋的——它让你跳舞，让你唱歌——但对我来说，还有一种我从未探索过的声音带来的兴奋，”他补充道。</p><p>回顾《What Ifs &amp; Maybes》——这张专辑为他带来了他的第二张英国冠军专辑——格伦南说：“这是我第一次想到：‘我不想仅仅成为一名创作型歌手’。它为我这张[新]专辑奠定了基础。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="这是基思·莱蒙 (Keith Lemon) 和汤姆·格伦南 (Tom Grennan) 在红地毯上闲逛 | 2022 年全英音乐奖" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fcRlVSR5cwg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/i-have-finally-caved-in-tom-grennan-releases-full-version-of-gillette-the-best-a-man-can-get-theme-song-3784454">格伦南正式发布了他完整版的吉列“The Best A Man Can Get”广告歌曲</a>。 “我终于屈服了，”他上个月在网上宣布这首歌时写道。</p><p>今年夏天，他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blossoms">Blossoms 的</a>支持下， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-grennan-announces-biggest-ever-headline-show-at-london-gunnersbury-park-buy-tickets-3492259">在伦敦的 Gunnersbury Park 举办了有史以来最盛大的头条演出</a>。</p><p>去年的“What Ifs &amp; Maybes”包含曲目<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-grennan-shares-most-personal-song-hes-ever-written-you-are-not-alone-3368104">“You Are Not Alone”</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-grennan-shares-new-single-here-tracklisting-and-release-date-for-what-ifs-maybes-3388557">“Here”</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/llisten-to-tom-grennan-new-single-remind-me-3185654">“Remind Me”</a> 、“AllThese Nights”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-tom-grennans-danceable-new-single-how-does-it-feel-3440175">“How Should It Feel”</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-tom-grennans-new-single-higher-3795435">聆听 Tom Grennan 令人振奋的新单曲“Higher”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
